 SYNTAX: [URL]|[Pre]|[SearchTerm] (Arg)

Common:
 [URL] = www.site.domain/specific/stuff
 [p|r|e] = [p]lay, [r]ead or [e]dit current list

One Argument:
 [URL]	→  play [URL]

Presets:
 [p]	→  Play through active playlist
 [r]	→  Read playlist
 [R]	→  Lists all playlists
 [e]	→  Edit playlist

Two Arguments:
 [URL] (a)	  → (a)dd [Link] to current playlist
 [SearchTerm] (f) → search playlist to (f)ind given [SearchTerm]
 [ListName] (p)	→  Picks playlist [ListName]
 [ListName] (P)	→  Creates playlist [ListName]
 [ListName] (K)	→  Deletes playlist [ListName]

 <q> exits active media, <ctrl+c> stops script
